      "date": "2014-08-13 02:39:38.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nif we fix this in libcfs firstly, then we can have:\n  cfs_time_seconds(int sec)\n  {\n       msecs_to_jiffies(sec * MSEC_PER_SEC);\n  }\n\nso we don't have two different approaches to convert seconds to jiffies:\n* cfs_time_seconds\n* msecs_to_jiffies",
